favorite fragrance.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">What are the main ingredients of the 200ml Beard Shampoo?<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>Our 200ml Beard Shampoo is a gentle cleanser with hydrating and soothing ingredients such as Aloe Vera, Argan Oil, Linseed Oil, and Castor Oil. These ingredients will keep your beard clean but not dry out your beard, enhanced with Vegan Fragrance oils for Scent.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">How often should I use beard Shampoo? <\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>For best results, apply beard Shampoo every two days, this will keep your beard clean and add additional moisture to your beard but you can adapt this depends on needs of your beard. <\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Can I use Beard Shampoo on a short beard?<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>Yes, of course, you can also use it on your head hair, its gentle cleanser with added hydration.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Is your beard Shampoo suitable for sensitive skin?<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>Yes, it's designed to be gentle and is suitable for all skin types, including sensitive skin. However, we recommend patch testing if you're concerned about allergies.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Does your Beard Shampoo contain nuts?<\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p>No, Our Beard shampoo does not contain nuts.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Is your Beard Shampoo Vegan and Cruetly Free? <\/button>\n<div class=\"panel\">\n  <p> Yes our Beard Shampoo are vegan and cruelty-free. We are committed to using only plant-based ingredients and \nSynethetic Fragrance oils, ensuring no animals are harmed or used in the production process. Additionally, our products are not tested on animals at any stage of product development. We are dedicated to providing high-quality, ethical products for our customers<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n<button class=\"accordion\">Scent List Description<\